data.description: Fantastic 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home with huge sunroom in popular Walnut Grove! Newer roof & HVAC! LVP flooring in main living areas! Carpet allowance! Living room with high ceilings! Dining room with updated light fixture! Kitchen with range, built in microwave, dishwasher, refrigerator, new sink/faucet & pantry! Breakfast room with bay window! Owners suite on main level with tray ceiling, bathroom with double sink vanity, soaking tub, separate shower, walk in closet & water closet! Two additional spare bedrooms on main level with nearby full bathroom! Upstairs 4th bedroom with full bathroom! Laundry room! Two car garage! Storage building stays! Extended patio & decking overlooking privacy fenced backyard, great for entertaining or enjoying everyday life! Great location with easy access to shopping, restaurants, I-20 & more!
